WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:900000,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:00:12.303 --> 00:00:14.264 position:50% align:center
[KEITA]
Oh! Nice pic!

00:00:14.347 --> 00:00:15.557 position:50% align:center
Thanks, Eitaro!

00:00:15.640 --> 00:00:16.933 position:50% align:center
No problem.

00:00:17.017 --> 00:00:18.184 position:50% align:center
Well, my ride's outside.

00:00:18.268 --> 00:00:20.020 position:50% align:center
[KOKI] Always getting
chauffeured around.

00:00:20.103 --> 00:00:22.272 position:50% align:center
Your family is
seriously supportive.

00:00:22.355 --> 00:00:23.565 position:50% align:center
[KEITA]
Thank you, Minato.

00:00:23.648 --> 00:00:24.941 position:50% align:center
[MINATO grunts]

00:00:25.025 --> 00:00:27.527 position:50% align:center
We're the best in Japan
because of you.

00:00:27.610 --> 00:00:29.029 position:50% align:center
[KEITA sniffs]

00:00:29.112 --> 00:00:31.197 position:50% align:center
I'm so lucky to be on your team!

00:00:31.281 --> 00:00:32.949 position:50% align:center
C'mon, man, cut it out.

00:00:33.033 --> 00:00:34.284 position:50% align:center
You know he's right!

00:00:34.367 --> 00:00:35.618 position:50% align:center
[MOMO] Minato!

00:00:35.702 --> 00:00:37.495 position:50% align:center
Just watch--I'm gonna
work to get on your level

00:00:37.579 --> 00:00:38.830 position:50% align:center
in high school.

00:00:38.913 --> 00:00:42.167 position:50% align:center
Then the two of us can
both be aces together!

00:00:42.250 --> 00:00:45.962 position:50% align:center
Yeah? Well, you better aim high,
'cause my level's on the rise!

00:00:46.046 --> 00:00:48.214 position:50% align:center
Sounds like we're gonna
have to keep you around, then.

00:00:48.298 --> 00:00:49.090 position:50% align:center
Damn right!

00:00:49.174 --> 00:00:52.010 position:50% align:center
[GROUP chuckles]

00:00:52.093 --> 00:00:55.430 position:50% align:center
[MINATO]
Am I dreaming?

00:00:55.513 --> 00:01:01.269 position:50% align:center
I remember this. It was right
before the car accident.

00:01:01.353 --> 00:01:02.604 position:50% align:center
[EITARO]
Minato?

00:01:02.687 --> 00:01:03.813 position:50% align:center
Time to wake up!

00:01:03.897 --> 00:01:05.190 position:50% align:center
[MINATO grunts]

00:01:06.191 --> 00:01:07.984 position:50% align:center
[EITARO]
Are you okay?

00:01:08.068 --> 00:01:11.237 position:50% align:center
Yeah... just had a nightmare.

00:01:11.321 --> 00:01:15.283 position:50% align:center
[GROUP snores]

00:01:15.367 --> 00:01:16.409 position:50% align:center
[EITARO]
Everyone decided to follow

00:01:16.493 --> 00:01:18.703 position:50% align:center
your lead and get a little rest.

00:01:23.500 --> 00:01:25.001 position:50% align:center
[MINATO]
Why didn't you sleep?

00:01:25.085 --> 00:01:28.380 position:50% align:center
I watched Shogakukan
and Rikka's game.

00:01:28.463 --> 00:01:31.091 position:50% align:center
It was 23 to zero.

00:01:31.174 --> 00:01:32.801 position:50% align:center
Even with Momo
out of commission,

00:01:32.884 --> 00:01:35.512 position:50% align:center
they completely
dominated the pool.

00:01:36.554 --> 00:01:37.639 position:50% align:center
I see.

00:01:38.890 --> 00:01:40.809 position:50% align:center
It's finally time.

00:01:40.892 --> 00:01:42.560 position:50% align:center
Uh-huh.

00:01:42.644 --> 00:01:43.895 position:50% align:center
I can't believe
I'm playing the guys

00:01:43.978 --> 00:01:46.523 position:50% align:center
I used to take photos of.

00:01:46.606 --> 00:01:48.274 position:50% align:center
That's why I don't
care if we lose.

00:01:48.358 --> 00:01:49.901 position:50% align:center
I'm just so happy to be here

00:01:49.984 --> 00:01:51.820 position:50% align:center
with you and
the guys by my side.

00:01:51.903 --> 00:01:53.029 position:50% align:center
Knock it off.

00:01:53.113 --> 00:01:55.490 position:50% align:center
You can be all happy
after we win the game.

00:01:55.573 --> 00:01:56.866 position:50% align:center
Okay.

00:01:58.326 --> 00:02:00.286 position:50% align:center
We have to beat them.

00:02:00.370 --> 00:02:02.622 position:50% align:center
We just have to.

00:02:02.706 --> 00:02:05.208 position:50% align:center
Hey! Everybody, get up!

00:02:05.291 --> 00:02:06.501 position:50% align:center
[GROUP groans]

00:02:06.584 --> 00:02:10.714 position:50% align:center
[MINATO] I said you
should nap, not hibernate!

00:02:10.797 --> 00:02:13.842 position:50% align:center
C'mon, let's get started.

00:02:15.885 --> 00:02:17.220 position:50% align:center
[ASUMI]
Hurry up, we're late!

00:02:17.303 --> 00:02:19.848 position:50% align:center
Are you absolutely sure
he told you we could come watch?

00:02:19.931 --> 00:02:22.809 position:50% align:center
Yup! I asked, and he said,
"You can if you want"!

00:02:22.892 --> 00:02:24.185 position:50% align:center
[HIDEKI, TAEKO] Huh?

00:02:24.269 --> 00:02:26.229 position:50% align:center
Obviously, he wants us here!

00:02:26.312 --> 00:02:27.480 position:50% align:center
Well...

00:02:27.564 --> 00:02:29.607 position:50% align:center
Hurry! It's starting!

00:02:34.738 --> 00:02:36.239 position:50% align:center
Made it!

00:02:38.366 --> 00:02:39.200 position:50% align:center
Best of luck.

00:02:39.284 --> 00:02:40.994 position:50% align:center
Oh! Thank you.

00:02:41.077 --> 00:02:42.704 position:50% align:center
Good luck.

00:02:42.787 --> 00:02:44.706 position:50% align:center
You, too.

00:02:44.789 --> 00:02:48.084 position:50% align:center
Gotta say, it's surreal looking
at you from the other side.

00:02:48.168 --> 00:02:51.755 position:50% align:center
I guess life really
is full of surprises.

00:02:51.838 --> 00:02:52.922 position:50% align:center
Good luck.

00:02:53.006 --> 00:02:55.091 position:50% align:center
I wish I could've
faced off against you.

00:02:55.175 --> 00:02:56.593 position:50% align:center
I'm game for a rain check.

00:02:56.676 --> 00:02:58.845 position:50% align:center
Are you guys seeing
how ripped this dude is?

00:02:58.928 --> 00:03:00.513 position:50% align:center
Yeah.

00:03:00.597 --> 00:03:02.724 position:50% align:center
[GROUP gasps]

00:03:02.807 --> 00:03:05.518 position:50% align:center
Same to you, Shugo. I'm sorry.

00:03:05.602 --> 00:03:08.980 position:50% align:center
[SHUGO] It's fine. I'm going
to do my best today regardless.

00:03:09.064 --> 00:03:10.023 position:50% align:center
[MOMO chuckles]

00:03:11.066 --> 00:03:15.362 position:50% align:center
Um, I dunno if you're still
thinking about going easy on us,

00:03:15.445 --> 00:03:17.864 position:50% align:center
but please play with
everything you've got.

00:03:17.947 --> 00:03:20.116 position:50% align:center
That was always the plan.

00:03:24.662 --> 00:03:25.997 position:50% align:center
[TAKESHI sniffs]

00:03:26.081 --> 00:03:28.500 position:50% align:center
Quit crying.
The game's about to start.

00:03:28.583 --> 00:03:31.544 position:50% align:center
It's just, I know I could've
played better than I did!

00:03:31.628 --> 00:03:33.129 position:50% align:center
You're our new captain,

00:03:33.213 --> 00:03:36.257 position:50% align:center
it's important that you study
our rivals for next year.

00:03:36.341 --> 00:03:37.759 position:50% align:center
Right.

00:03:38.760 --> 00:03:42.472 position:50% align:center
[MASAMI] Wait. Hey, Anna aren't
you ball handler this game?

00:03:42.555 --> 00:03:45.266 position:50% align:center
[ANNA grunts] Chinu told me
she wanted to do it instead.

00:03:45.350 --> 00:03:46.601 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:03:47.894 --> 00:03:52.482 position:50% align:center
[CHINU] Come on, Minato.
Show me you've really changed.

00:03:55.652 --> 00:03:56.820 position:50% align:center
[MINATO grunts]

00:04:29.519 --> 00:04:32.105 position:50% align:center
[ASUMI]
You can do this, Minato!

00:04:32.188 --> 00:04:33.898 position:50% align:center
[whistle sounds]

00:04:40.196 --> 00:04:41.364 position:50% align:center
[EITARO]
Right.

00:04:41.448 --> 00:04:44.409 position:50% align:center
Okay, gang, let's walk
through our game plan.

00:04:44.492 --> 00:04:47.620 position:50% align:center
We'll move Amiami
to flat and Buu to wing.

00:04:47.704 --> 00:04:50.498 position:50% align:center
That way Amiami can
switch to defense easier.

00:04:50.582 --> 00:04:52.500 position:50% align:center
If an opponent gets
past the rest of us,

00:04:52.584 --> 00:04:53.835 position:50% align:center
we need you to chase them.

00:04:53.918 --> 00:04:54.711 position:50% align:center
[SHUGO]
Got it.

00:04:54.794 --> 00:04:56.504 position:50% align:center
[JO]
Minato, Eitaro, and Buu,

00:04:56.588 --> 00:04:58.173 position:50% align:center
you guys will
head up our offense.

00:04:58.256 --> 00:05:00.091 position:50% align:center
[GROUP grunts]

00:05:00.175 --> 00:05:01.009 position:50% align:center
[EITARO grunts]

00:05:01.092 --> 00:05:02.927 position:50% align:center
[TAKEKAZU grunts]

00:05:05.263 --> 00:05:07.098 position:50% align:center
[MINATO]
He's on me!

00:05:07.182 --> 00:05:08.224 position:50% align:center
It's been a while
since I've practiced

00:05:08.308 --> 00:05:10.852 position:50% align:center
with Koki as my defender.

00:05:10.935 --> 00:05:13.438 position:50% align:center
I can't get away.

00:05:13.521 --> 00:05:16.024 position:50% align:center
But that doesn't
mean I can't score!

00:05:17.192 --> 00:05:18.151 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:05:18.234 --> 00:05:19.110 position:50% align:center
[KEITA grunts]

00:05:19.194 --> 00:05:20.111 position:50% align:center
[GROUP gasps]

00:05:20.195 --> 00:05:21.613 position:50% align:center
So close!

00:05:21.696 --> 00:05:22.989 position:50% align:center
No!

00:05:25.033 --> 00:05:26.493 position:50% align:center
[MOMO grunts]

00:05:29.204 --> 00:05:32.207 position:50% align:center
[SHUGO] Remember the plan!
Focus on defense!

00:05:32.290 --> 00:05:35.043 position:50% align:center
[BABAYARO] Gotta protect
the goal. I can do this!

00:05:35.126 --> 00:05:38.588 position:50% align:center
[YOSHIHARU] This time
I won't drag the team down.

00:05:38.672 --> 00:05:40.465 position:50% align:center
[YOSHIHARU grunts]

00:05:40.548 --> 00:05:41.716 position:50% align:center
[MITSUI]
Here!

00:05:45.512 --> 00:05:46.846 position:50% align:center
[MOMO]
Uh?

00:05:46.930 --> 00:05:48.390 position:50% align:center
[YOSHIHARU]
Thank goodness.

00:05:48.473 --> 00:05:50.183 position:50% align:center
[MITSUI grunts]

00:05:50.266 --> 00:05:52.477 position:50% align:center
[JO]
Hell yeah! The plan worked!

00:05:52.560 --> 00:05:53.728 position:50% align:center
[JO yells]

00:05:55.772 --> 00:05:57.982 position:50% align:center
[EITARO grunts]

00:05:58.066 --> 00:06:00.944 position:50% align:center
How'd you like
a taste of my arm?!

00:06:01.027 --> 00:06:02.487 position:50% align:center
[yells]

00:06:04.364 --> 00:06:05.657 position:50% align:center
[GROUP gasps]

00:06:13.289 --> 00:06:16.209 position:50% align:center
[WATER POLO PLAYERS grunting]

00:06:28.596 --> 00:06:30.181 position:50% align:center
[TAKEKAZU growls]

00:06:31.474 --> 00:06:32.392 position:50% align:center
[TAKEKAZU gasps]

00:06:32.475 --> 00:06:34.686 position:50% align:center
[whistle sounds]

00:06:34.769 --> 00:06:35.979 position:50% align:center
An ejection?!

00:06:36.062 --> 00:06:37.731 position:50% align:center
Huh?!

00:06:37.814 --> 00:06:40.442 position:50% align:center
[MINATO] He stopped on
purpose so Ejiri would foul him!

00:06:40.525 --> 00:06:43.737 position:50% align:center
Ejection? Ah.

00:06:43.820 --> 00:06:47.032 position:50% align:center
"The player who caused the foul
must swim to the exclusion zone

00:06:47.115 --> 00:06:49.659 position:50% align:center
and stay there for
at least 20 seconds.

00:06:49.743 --> 00:06:52.120 position:50% align:center
They cannot rejoin the game
until that time has passed

00:06:52.203 --> 00:06:54.497 position:50% align:center
or the ball changes possession."

00:06:54.581 --> 00:06:56.499 position:50% align:center
Uh-oh. That doesn't sound good!

00:06:56.583 --> 00:06:58.752 position:50% align:center
C'mon, defense!
Put your hands up!

00:06:58.835 --> 00:07:00.045 position:50% align:center
[GROUP grunts]

00:07:01.338 --> 00:07:02.547 position:50% align:center
[KOKI grunts]

00:07:06.134 --> 00:07:09.137 position:50% align:center
[BABAYARO pants, grunts]

00:07:09.763 --> 00:07:11.264 position:50% align:center
[JO]
Our ball!

00:07:15.268 --> 00:07:16.686 position:50% align:center
Hey!

00:07:20.648 --> 00:07:23.693 position:50% align:center
[panting]

00:07:23.777 --> 00:07:25.153 position:50% align:center
[EITARO grunts]

00:07:29.282 --> 00:07:30.367 position:50% align:center
[KEITA grunts]

00:07:31.993 --> 00:07:33.119 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:07:34.871 --> 00:07:35.413 position:50% align:center
[KEITA grunts]

00:07:35.497 --> 00:07:36.790 position:50% align:center
[GROUP gasps]

00:07:37.874 --> 00:07:40.669 position:50% align:center
Get back! Stop their counter!

00:07:40.752 --> 00:07:43.922 position:50% align:center
[GROUP gasping]

00:07:44.005 --> 00:07:47.425 position:50% align:center
They haven't slowed down
since the game started.

00:07:47.509 --> 00:07:49.469 position:50% align:center
I'm sure they're getting tired.

00:07:50.553 --> 00:07:52.138 position:50% align:center
[panting]

00:07:52.222 --> 00:07:54.557 position:50% align:center
[panting]

00:07:54.641 --> 00:07:56.559 position:50% align:center
[TAKEKAZU gasps]

00:07:56.643 --> 00:07:58.853 position:50% align:center
[EITARO grunting]

00:08:01.981 --> 00:08:04.442 position:50% align:center
Gotta win!

00:08:06.403 --> 00:08:11.408 position:50% align:center
[WATER POLO PLAYERS grunting]

00:08:14.911 --> 00:08:17.664 position:50% align:center
[MINATO]
Time's almost up!

00:08:17.747 --> 00:08:18.873 position:50% align:center
[KEITA grunts]

00:08:18.957 --> 00:08:20.834 position:50% align:center
[buzzer sounds]

00:08:20.917 --> 00:08:22.961 position:50% align:center
[CROWD chatters]

00:08:23.044 --> 00:08:25.505 position:50% align:center
I can't believe they're
tied at zero to zero!

00:08:25.588 --> 00:08:27.716 position:50% align:center
This is the most
intense game ever!

00:08:27.799 --> 00:08:29.092 position:50% align:center
[TAEKO exhales]

00:08:29.175 --> 00:08:30.593 position:50% align:center
Did you forget to breathe, too?

00:08:30.677 --> 00:08:32.470 position:50% align:center
[TAEKO, ASUMI]
Mm!

00:08:32.554 --> 00:08:35.849 position:50% align:center
This is gonna make me cry again!

00:08:35.932 --> 00:08:37.892 position:50% align:center
Enough with the waterworks.

00:08:37.976 --> 00:08:40.228 position:50% align:center
That said, I get it.

00:08:40.311 --> 00:08:41.980 position:50% align:center
Me, too.

00:08:42.063 --> 00:08:43.982 position:50% align:center
C'mon, please! Put me in!

00:08:44.065 --> 00:08:45.734 position:50% align:center
I told you, no! It's not safe.

00:08:45.817 --> 00:08:46.943 position:50% align:center
I won't push it, swear!

00:08:47.027 --> 00:08:49.612 position:50% align:center
But I have to try
and put a stop to this!

00:08:51.531 --> 00:08:54.367 position:50% align:center
What Koki's doing is wrong,
and you know it.

00:08:54.451 --> 00:08:55.827 position:50% align:center
[BIZEN grunts]

00:08:58.163 --> 00:08:59.622 position:50% align:center
[CHINU grunts]

00:08:59.706 --> 00:09:02.042 position:50% align:center
[JO] Hot damn, guys!

00:09:02.125 --> 00:09:03.585 position:50% align:center
You've been killing it so far,
keep it up!

00:09:03.668 --> 00:09:05.962 position:50% align:center
--[GROUP] Yeah!
--[EITARO] Okay!

00:09:06.046 --> 00:09:07.714 position:50% align:center
[YOSHIHARU]
They're playing so well.

00:09:07.797 --> 00:09:10.342 position:50% align:center
Why can't I keep up?

00:09:10.425 --> 00:09:11.593 position:50% align:center
[MINATO]
You okay?

00:09:11.676 --> 00:09:14.346 position:50% align:center
[YOSHIHARU]
Huh? Yeah, fine.

00:09:14.429 --> 00:09:17.640 position:50% align:center
I still have a ton of energy,
so feel free to pass it to me.

00:09:17.724 --> 00:09:20.685 position:50% align:center
Yeah, you can say that again.
You're all fired up.

00:09:20.769 --> 00:09:21.770 position:50% align:center
Big time.

00:09:21.853 --> 00:09:24.064 position:50% align:center
Probably because
I had a little boost.

00:09:24.147 --> 00:09:24.939 position:50% align:center
[BABAYARO, JO]
A boost?

00:09:25.023 --> 00:09:26.608 position:50% align:center
Right, Babayaro?

00:09:26.691 --> 00:09:28.777 position:50% align:center
Oh... Yeah!

00:09:28.860 --> 00:09:31.780 position:50% align:center
Hey. You got any more
of those things you made?

00:09:31.863 --> 00:09:33.573 position:50% align:center
[BABAYARO gasps]
Mm-hm!

00:09:33.656 --> 00:09:37.327 position:50% align:center
[BABAYARO] Before the match,
he ate one of my chocolates!

00:09:37.410 --> 00:09:40.622 position:50% align:center
Really? Thought you said
no snacks before games!

00:09:40.705 --> 00:09:41.956 position:50% align:center
I thought if I ate one, too,

00:09:42.040 --> 00:09:43.792 position:50% align:center
it might help bring us
together as a team.

00:09:43.875 --> 00:09:46.586 position:50% align:center
Damn, who are you and
what've you done with Minato?

00:09:46.670 --> 00:09:49.047 position:50% align:center
[MINATO]
Shut up!

00:09:49.130 --> 00:09:51.466 position:50% align:center
I realized something
important today.

00:09:51.549 --> 00:09:53.385 position:50% align:center
There are a lot
of ways you can win.

00:09:53.468 --> 00:09:54.427 position:50% align:center
But for our team, we need--

00:09:54.511 --> 00:09:56.680 position:50% align:center
[EITARO]
Whoa! Guys, look!

00:09:56.763 --> 00:09:58.181 position:50% align:center
[GROUP]
Hm?

00:10:02.936 --> 00:10:05.230 position:50% align:center
[EITARO] They're putting
Momo in the game.

00:10:07.899 --> 00:10:10.610 position:50% align:center
Oh, damn, the final boss!

00:10:10.694 --> 00:10:12.529 position:50% align:center
[SHUGO]
This is my chance!

00:10:13.947 --> 00:10:17.200 position:50% align:center
[MINATO]
Okay, Momo. Bring it on!

00:10:22.038 --> 00:10:24.416 position:50% align:center
[SHUGO]
I have to beat him to the ball!

00:10:26.876 --> 00:10:28.169 position:50% align:center
[MOMO grunts]

00:10:31.381 --> 00:10:33.258 position:50% align:center
[SHUGO]
This is it.

00:10:33.341 --> 00:10:35.885 position:50% align:center
After all these years,

00:10:35.969 --> 00:10:38.346 position:50% align:center
I can finally win!

00:10:41.516 --> 00:10:43.309 position:50% align:center
[MOMO grunts]

00:10:43.393 --> 00:10:44.477 position:50% align:center
[MOMO]
Let's go!

00:10:44.561 --> 00:10:45.854 position:50% align:center
[SHUGO gasps]

00:10:52.068 --> 00:10:54.195 position:50% align:center
[JO gasps]

00:10:54.279 --> 00:10:56.031 position:50% align:center
[whistle sounds]

00:10:57.824 --> 00:10:58.950 position:50% align:center
[MINATO grunts]

00:11:00.201 --> 00:11:02.203 position:50% align:center
[MOMO chuckles]

00:11:02.287 --> 00:11:03.621 position:50% align:center
[SHUGO grunts]

00:11:07.208 --> 00:11:09.169 position:50% align:center
[MINATO] Quit making those
faces.

00:11:09.252 --> 00:11:11.087 position:50% align:center
I'm gonna score and tie us up!

00:11:13.965 --> 00:11:14.799 position:50% align:center
[TAKEKAZU grunts]

00:11:14.883 --> 00:11:16.384 position:50% align:center
[whistle sounds]

00:11:16.468 --> 00:11:17.552 position:50% align:center
[MINATO grunts]

00:11:22.724 --> 00:11:24.559 position:50% align:center
[BOTH grunting]

00:11:28.605 --> 00:11:31.316 position:50% align:center
[grunts, yells]

00:11:31.399 --> 00:11:33.818 position:50% align:center
[KOKI grunts, gasps]

00:11:33.902 --> 00:11:37.864 position:50% align:center
[MINATO] What happened to him?
He was nothing like this before!

00:11:39.532 --> 00:11:40.950 position:50% align:center
[KOKI grunts]

00:11:44.329 --> 00:11:47.374 position:50% align:center
[MOMO]
Koki! Quit holding back on them!

00:11:47.457 --> 00:11:48.792 position:50% align:center
[KOKI]
I'm not, I swear!

00:11:48.875 --> 00:11:50.960 position:50% align:center
Oh, what, so that was your best?

00:11:51.044 --> 00:11:54.422 position:50% align:center
Come on, do you even
want to beat Minato?

00:11:54.506 --> 00:11:57.008 position:50% align:center
I-I... I don't know.

00:11:57.092 --> 00:11:58.343 position:50% align:center
--[KEITA gasps]
--[MOMO grunts]

00:11:58.426 --> 00:12:01.888 position:50% align:center
[KOKI] I knew he wouldn't
be the same as before.

00:12:01.971 --> 00:12:05.725 position:50% align:center
But h-he's so much
weaker than I ever imagined.

00:12:05.809 --> 00:12:09.479 position:50% align:center
It doesn't feel fair to play
against him when he's like this.

00:12:09.562 --> 00:12:11.523 position:50% align:center
Yeah, well, that's not an
excuse to go easy on him!

00:12:11.606 --> 00:12:12.649 position:50% align:center
I know, but--!

00:12:12.732 --> 00:12:14.067 position:50% align:center
[KEITA]
I get it.

00:12:15.110 --> 00:12:18.029 position:50% align:center
[KEITA] He's back,
but not in the way we knew him.

00:12:18.113 --> 00:12:19.614 position:50% align:center
It sucks.

00:12:19.698 --> 00:12:23.785 position:50% align:center
It puts a hole in your chest and
stops you from doing your best.

00:12:25.745 --> 00:12:28.123 position:50% align:center
But out of respect
for our old friend,

00:12:28.206 --> 00:12:31.167 position:50% align:center
we need to play them with
everything that we've got.

00:12:33.253 --> 00:12:35.171 position:50% align:center
[KOKI]
Mm...

00:12:35.255 --> 00:12:37.215 position:50% align:center
Let's go give it our all!

00:12:40.969 --> 00:12:42.470 position:50% align:center
[MINATO]
Get back here!

00:12:44.305 --> 00:12:46.433 position:50% align:center
Hey!

00:12:46.516 --> 00:12:47.559 position:50% align:center
[BABAYARO grunts]

00:12:47.642 --> 00:12:48.560 position:50% align:center
[MOMO grunts]

00:12:48.643 --> 00:12:49.561 position:50% align:center
[JO gasps]

00:12:49.644 --> 00:12:51.438 position:50% align:center
--[whistle sounds]
--[MINATO gasps]

00:12:55.650 --> 00:12:59.362 position:50% align:center
[WATER POLO PLAYERS grunting]

00:13:12.792 --> 00:13:14.252 position:50% align:center
So, this was their plan.

00:13:14.336 --> 00:13:17.672 position:50% align:center
During the first period they
must've been testing the waters.

00:13:17.756 --> 00:13:21.760 position:50% align:center
By now Yamanami must
be worn out... We would be.

00:13:21.843 --> 00:13:23.720 position:50% align:center
[TAKESHI]
Just score one freakin' point!

00:13:23.803 --> 00:13:25.430 position:50% align:center
[AKIHISA, NORIMICHI grunt]

00:13:25.513 --> 00:13:28.516 position:50% align:center
[TAKESHI]
Please! Do it for us!

00:13:31.686 --> 00:13:33.730 position:50% align:center
Hey.

00:13:33.813 --> 00:13:36.816 position:50% align:center
Chin up, team.
Don't look so down.

00:13:36.900 --> 00:13:39.069 position:50% align:center
What's our plan to
turn things around?

00:13:39.152 --> 00:13:40.487 position:50% align:center
Any thoughts?

00:13:40.570 --> 00:13:41.946 position:50% align:center
None here.

00:13:42.030 --> 00:13:43.907 position:50% align:center
But wait!

00:13:43.990 --> 00:13:45.075 position:50% align:center
Minato!

00:13:45.158 --> 00:13:46.201 position:50% align:center
[MINATO]
Hm?

00:13:46.284 --> 00:13:48.161 position:50% align:center
Remember what the old you said?

00:13:48.244 --> 00:13:50.121 position:50% align:center
Something about how
our team is our strength,

00:13:50.205 --> 00:13:52.457 position:50% align:center
and as long as we all
work together, we'll win?

00:13:52.540 --> 00:13:53.833 position:50% align:center
That's right.

00:13:53.917 --> 00:13:55.085 position:50% align:center
Well, I agree!

00:13:55.168 --> 00:13:56.127 position:50% align:center
Same here!

00:13:56.211 --> 00:13:56.753 position:50% align:center
Yeah!

00:13:56.836 --> 00:13:57.545 position:50% align:center
For sure!

00:13:57.629 --> 00:13:58.380 position:50% align:center
[YOSHIHARU]
Mm-hm!

00:13:58.463 --> 00:14:00.256 position:50% align:center
Me, too.

00:14:00.340 --> 00:14:02.425 position:50% align:center
Then let's do
this thing together!

00:14:02.509 --> 00:14:03.551 position:50% align:center
[GROUP]
Yeah!

00:14:03.635 --> 00:14:05.720 position:50% align:center
--[MINATO chuckles]
--[whistle sounds]

00:14:13.687 --> 00:14:15.063 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:14:15.146 --> 00:14:16.731 position:50% align:center
[MOMO, BABYARO grunt]

00:14:16.815 --> 00:14:18.108 position:50% align:center
[TAKEKAZU grunts]

00:14:18.191 --> 00:14:19.984 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:14:20.068 --> 00:14:21.361 position:50% align:center
[MINATO grunts]

00:14:21.444 --> 00:14:23.405 position:50% align:center
[JO grunts]

00:14:23.488 --> 00:14:24.864 position:50% align:center
[BIZEN]
Mm...

00:14:30.328 --> 00:14:31.788 position:50% align:center
--[MOMO grunts]
--[JO gasps]

00:14:31.871 --> 00:14:33.623 position:50% align:center
[whistle sounds]

00:14:37.961 --> 00:14:41.089 position:50% align:center
[CHINU] Thirty-seven seconds
left in the final period,

00:14:41.172 --> 00:14:43.133 position:50% align:center
and it's 15 to zero.

00:14:44.259 --> 00:14:45.218 position:50% align:center
[CHINU]
What could possibly

00:14:45.301 --> 00:14:47.012 position:50% align:center
be going through
your head right now?

00:15:02.652 --> 00:15:04.029 position:50% align:center
[MINATO]
This is such bullshit!

00:15:04.112 --> 00:15:05.488 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:15:05.572 --> 00:15:07.741 position:50% align:center
I am sick and tired of being
held back by you amateurs!

00:15:07.824 --> 00:15:09.617 position:50% align:center
Gimme a break!

00:15:09.701 --> 00:15:12.037 position:50% align:center
How dare you make me
look so pathetic?!

00:15:12.120 --> 00:15:15.040 position:50% align:center
It's simple:
just pass the ball to me.

00:15:15.123 --> 00:15:16.666 position:50% align:center
I'll do the scoring!

00:15:16.750 --> 00:15:19.210 position:50% align:center
What the hell's wrong with you?!

00:15:19.294 --> 00:15:21.296 position:50% align:center
Looks like you're
still a jerk after all!

00:15:21.379 --> 00:15:22.881 position:50% align:center
What?!

00:15:22.964 --> 00:15:26.009 position:50% align:center
[REFEREE 12A] Stop that right
now or you'll forfeit the match.

00:15:26.092 --> 00:15:28.303 position:50% align:center
You are so useless!

00:15:28.386 --> 00:15:29.888 position:50% align:center
[ASUMI, TAEKO, HIDEKI grunt]

00:15:31.556 --> 00:15:33.308 position:50% align:center
Screw that guy!

00:15:36.686 --> 00:15:38.063 position:50% align:center
[whistle sounds]

00:15:39.647 --> 00:15:42.025 position:50% align:center
[EITARO grunts]

00:15:43.151 --> 00:15:46.321 position:50% align:center
[YOSHIHARU gasping]

00:15:48.573 --> 00:15:51.242 position:50% align:center
[WATER POLO PLAYERS grunting]

00:15:51.785 --> 00:15:53.411 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:15:53.495 --> 00:15:55.163 position:50% align:center
[MOMO grunts]

00:15:55.246 --> 00:15:57.665 position:50% align:center
[MOMO yells]

00:15:57.749 --> 00:15:59.542 position:50% align:center
[JO yells]

00:16:02.545 --> 00:16:04.255 position:50% align:center
[BABAYARO grunts]

00:16:06.007 --> 00:16:07.550 position:50% align:center
I got it!

00:16:15.600 --> 00:16:17.310 position:50% align:center
[TAKEKAZU grunts]

00:16:17.394 --> 00:16:18.603 position:50% align:center
[EITARO grunts]

00:16:21.356 --> 00:16:23.650 position:50% align:center
[MINATO grunting]

00:16:27.821 --> 00:16:29.698 position:50% align:center
[SHUGO]
Now's my chance!

00:16:29.781 --> 00:16:31.574 position:50% align:center
I'm gonna beat him!

00:16:31.658 --> 00:16:35.995 position:50% align:center
[SHUGO yells]

00:16:36.079 --> 00:16:38.498 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:16:38.581 --> 00:16:39.874 position:50% align:center
[EITARO grunts]

00:16:42.252 --> 00:16:43.420 position:50% align:center
Watch out!

00:16:43.503 --> 00:16:44.713 position:50% align:center
[MINATO grunts]

00:16:44.796 --> 00:16:47.132 position:50% align:center
[yells]

00:16:52.721 --> 00:16:58.727 position:50% align:center
[KEITA]
There it is. It's his feint!

00:16:58.810 --> 00:17:01.980 position:50% align:center
[KEITA] Sorry, but
that won't work on me!

00:17:05.525 --> 00:17:06.443 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:17:06.526 --> 00:17:07.694 position:50% align:center
[KOKI, MOMO gasp]

00:17:07.777 --> 00:17:09.112 position:50% align:center
[CHINU gasps]

00:17:11.114 --> 00:17:14.868 position:50% align:center
[panting]

00:17:14.951 --> 00:17:16.745 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:17:16.828 --> 00:17:18.496 position:50% align:center
[yells]

00:17:20.749 --> 00:17:22.500 position:50% align:center
[KEITA gasps]

00:17:22.584 --> 00:17:25.712 position:50% align:center
[GROUP gasping]

00:17:31.676 --> 00:17:33.386 position:50% align:center
[whistle sounds]

00:17:33.470 --> 00:17:36.139 position:50% align:center
[GROUP]
Yeah!

00:17:36.222 --> 00:17:37.640 position:50% align:center
[CHINU gasps]

00:17:38.808 --> 00:17:39.851 position:50% align:center
Wha--?!

00:17:39.934 --> 00:17:40.977 position:50% align:center
[ASUMI, TAEKO, HIDEKI cheer]

00:17:41.061 --> 00:17:42.645 position:50% align:center
[YOSHIHARU'S MOTHER sniffs]

00:17:42.729 --> 00:17:43.855 position:50% align:center
[EITARO'S SISTER,
EITARO'S MOTHER cheer]

00:17:43.938 --> 00:17:45.148 position:50% align:center
[BABAYARO'S FATHER,
BABAYARO'S MOTHER cheer]

00:17:45.231 --> 00:17:46.524 position:50% align:center
Yeah!

00:17:46.608 --> 00:17:48.485 position:50% align:center
--[TAKESHI, NORIMICHI cheer]
--[AKIHISA] Way to go!

00:17:48.568 --> 00:17:50.278 position:50% align:center
That was incredible, Ushi!

00:17:50.362 --> 00:17:51.613 position:50% align:center
[YOSHIHARU chuckles]

00:17:51.696 --> 00:17:53.615 position:50% align:center
[JO]
You did it! The Ushimado Shout!

00:17:53.698 --> 00:17:54.866 position:50% align:center
The what?

00:17:54.949 --> 00:17:57.118 position:50% align:center
You told me to
yell when I shoot.

00:17:57.202 --> 00:17:59.704 position:50% align:center
It gives me power.

00:17:59.788 --> 00:18:00.955 position:50% align:center
I see.

00:18:01.039 --> 00:18:02.582 position:50% align:center
Must've been the other me.

00:18:02.665 --> 00:18:03.500 position:50% align:center
[TAKEKAZU]
Hey, Minato!

00:18:03.583 --> 00:18:04.918 position:50% align:center
Uh?

00:18:05.001 --> 00:18:07.379 position:50% align:center
What was up with you
being such a jackass?!

00:18:07.462 --> 00:18:08.672 position:50% align:center
Sorry 'bout that.

00:18:08.755 --> 00:18:10.715 position:50% align:center
I was trying to draw
their defenders toward me.

00:18:10.799 --> 00:18:12.300 position:50% align:center
Well, you could have told us!

00:18:12.384 --> 00:18:14.678 position:50% align:center
[EITARO] If he did that,
his plan wouldn't have worked.

00:18:14.761 --> 00:18:16.179 position:50% align:center
[BABAYARO]
He's got a point.

00:18:16.262 --> 00:18:17.555 position:50% align:center
Oh, yeah.

00:18:17.639 --> 00:18:18.556 position:50% align:center
Sharp as ever.

00:18:18.640 --> 00:18:19.933 position:50% align:center
Hey, who asked you, man?

00:18:20.016 --> 00:18:22.060 position:50% align:center
[JO, EITARO, BABAYARO laugh]

00:18:22.143 --> 00:18:23.353 position:50% align:center
[TAKEKAZU]
It's not funny!

00:18:23.436 --> 00:18:26.314 position:50% align:center
[MINATO] Even though
we lost, I feel happy.

00:18:26.398 --> 00:18:28.483 position:50% align:center
That's a first.

00:18:28.566 --> 00:18:33.196 position:50% align:center
I didn't score a single point,
but I'm still so proud.

00:18:38.576 --> 00:18:39.703 position:50% align:center
[KEITA]
Good game.

00:18:39.786 --> 00:18:40.829 position:50% align:center
Yeah.

00:18:40.912 --> 00:18:42.831 position:50% align:center
You really fooled
us with that one.

00:18:42.914 --> 00:18:44.165 position:50% align:center
Guess so.

00:18:44.249 --> 00:18:46.084 position:50% align:center
But we'll be ready for
all your tricks next time.

00:18:46.167 --> 00:18:47.168 position:50% align:center
What he said!

00:18:47.252 --> 00:18:48.962 position:50% align:center
[MINATO]
Hey, shouldn't that be my line?

00:18:49.045 --> 00:18:51.673 position:50% align:center
You guys totally stomped us,
ever heard of mercy?

00:18:51.756 --> 00:18:58.054 position:50% align:center
[GROUP laughing]

00:18:58.138 --> 00:18:59.472 position:50% align:center
[chuckles]

00:18:59.556 --> 00:19:01.766 position:50% align:center
[REFEREE 12A] All right,
game's over! Out of the pool!

00:19:01.850 --> 00:19:03.601 position:50% align:center
--[MOMO] Yeah, yeah.
--[KOKI, KEITA] Right.

00:19:04.686 --> 00:19:06.146 position:50% align:center
[MOMO]
Hey, Shugo!

00:19:08.314 --> 00:19:09.691 position:50% align:center
You're pretty fast.

00:19:11.443 --> 00:19:13.153 position:50% align:center
I know.

00:19:13.236 --> 00:19:14.487 position:50% align:center
[MOMO chuckles]

00:19:15.488 --> 00:19:16.906 position:50% align:center
[SHUGO chuckles]

00:19:24.205 --> 00:19:25.373 position:50% align:center
Nice work.

00:19:25.457 --> 00:19:26.958 position:50% align:center
[MINATO chuckles]

00:19:32.839 --> 00:19:35.008 position:50% align:center
How's your leg
feeling? You good?

00:19:35.091 --> 00:19:37.135 position:50% align:center
[MOMO]
Yes, sir.

00:19:37.218 --> 00:19:38.636 position:50% align:center
[BIZEN]
Momosaki.

00:19:38.720 --> 00:19:40.013 position:50% align:center
Yeah?

00:19:40.096 --> 00:19:42.724 position:50% align:center
You played well today. Be proud.

00:19:42.807 --> 00:19:44.351 position:50% align:center
You're your own kind of ace.

00:19:44.434 --> 00:19:46.936 position:50% align:center
And you deserve so
much praise for that.

00:19:48.355 --> 00:19:49.939 position:50% align:center
Thanks!

00:19:52.734 --> 00:19:54.569 position:50% align:center
[MASAMI]
Hey, Chinu!

00:19:56.237 --> 00:19:57.906 position:50% align:center
Could you talk to
the first years for me?

00:19:57.989 --> 00:19:59.532 position:50% align:center
A bunch of them were
supposed to be here

00:19:59.616 --> 00:20:01.409 position:50% align:center
and decided not to
show up. I tried to--

00:20:01.493 --> 00:20:03.536 position:50% align:center
[CHINU] No, you're
gonna have to handle it!

00:20:03.620 --> 00:20:04.913 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:20:04.996 --> 00:20:06.998 position:50% align:center
I know I'm usually
the one who helps

00:20:07.082 --> 00:20:09.876 position:50% align:center
but I already have
a ton on my plate.

00:20:09.959 --> 00:20:11.586 position:50% align:center
I need to focus on myself.

00:20:11.670 --> 00:20:13.254 position:50% align:center
So can you take
care of it, please?

00:20:13.338 --> 00:20:15.090 position:50% align:center
[MASAMI]
Uh...

00:20:15.173 --> 00:20:18.551 position:50% align:center
I've decided that
I want to change, too.

00:20:18.635 --> 00:20:20.345 position:50% align:center
[MASAMI]
What?

00:20:28.436 --> 00:20:30.438 position:50% align:center
Oh, so did your band win?

00:20:30.522 --> 00:20:32.315 position:50% align:center
No, runners-up.

00:20:32.399 --> 00:20:33.566 position:50% align:center
That's amazing.

00:20:33.650 --> 00:20:34.651 position:50% align:center
No, it isn't.

00:20:34.734 --> 00:20:36.903 position:50% align:center
We don't go on to nationals.

00:20:38.905 --> 00:20:40.907 position:50% align:center
But how did you do today?

00:20:40.990 --> 00:20:41.825 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:20:41.908 --> 00:20:43.660 position:50% align:center
[MINATO]
Did you play your best?

00:20:43.743 --> 00:20:45.745 position:50% align:center
[ASUMI]
Hmm... I think.

00:20:45.829 --> 00:20:47.080 position:50% align:center
[MINATO]
That's a huge deal.

00:20:47.163 --> 00:20:48.498 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:20:50.083 --> 00:20:51.835 position:50% align:center
Yeah, it is!

00:20:51.918 --> 00:20:53.586 position:50% align:center
[HIDEKI, TAEKO chuckle]

00:20:53.670 --> 00:20:54.713 position:50% align:center
[MINATO]
Hey, uh, Mom?

00:20:54.796 --> 00:20:56.297 position:50% align:center
[TAEKO]
Hm?

00:20:56.381 --> 00:20:58.383 position:50% align:center
[MINATO]
I really do love water polo.

00:20:58.466 --> 00:20:59.926 position:50% align:center
[TAEKO]
What?

00:21:00.010 --> 00:21:02.679 position:50% align:center
[MINATO] You said you want me
to do what makes me happy.

00:21:02.762 --> 00:21:08.268 position:50% align:center
And I am. So please don't worry
about the accident, okay?

00:21:08.351 --> 00:21:10.687 position:50% align:center
[TAEKO gasps]

00:21:10.770 --> 00:21:14.357 position:50% align:center
[TAEKO cries]

00:21:14.441 --> 00:21:15.567 position:50% align:center
[HIDEKI]
Mm.

00:21:17.444 --> 00:21:18.653 position:50% align:center
[ASUMI grunts]

00:21:27.704 --> 00:21:30.999 position:50% align:center
[EITARO yells] I was so
riled up, I couldn't even sleep!

00:21:31.082 --> 00:21:31.916 position:50% align:center
Same here.

00:21:32.000 --> 00:21:33.293 position:50% align:center
We got dunked on
that whole time,

00:21:33.376 --> 00:21:35.170 position:50% align:center
only to score one measly point!

00:21:35.253 --> 00:21:36.755 position:50% align:center
That's weird;
I slept like a baby.

00:21:36.838 --> 00:21:37.547 position:50% align:center
Me, too.

00:21:37.630 --> 00:21:38.340 position:50% align:center
[YOSHIHARU]
Same here.

00:21:38.423 --> 00:21:39.507 position:50% align:center
[TAKEKAZU]
For real?

00:21:39.591 --> 00:21:42.635 position:50% align:center
Yeah, don't worry.
We'll get 'em next time!

00:21:42.719 --> 00:21:44.095 position:50% align:center
[GROUP]
Yeah!

00:21:44.179 --> 00:21:45.305 position:50% align:center
[SHUGO]
For that to happen...

